{"title":"The new Velo Orange Crazy Bar handlebar is… well, just look at it","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/velo-orange-crazy-bar/","date":1612523359000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><section itemprop=\"articleBody\"><p>The <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/brand/velo-orange/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Velo Orange</a> Crazy Bar is a three-piece flat <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/what-is-a-touring-bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">touring</a> handlebar with integrated aero-ish extensions. It has been updated with a new shape for 2021 and is expected to ship in June.</p><p>The Crazy Bar has been in Velo Orange’s lineup for eight years now and has received numerous updates along the way. This iteration features the most significant changes yet and has been developed following community feedback and extensive in-house testing.</p><h2>What’s new with the Velo Orange Crazy Bar?</h2><div><picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-2-c9d1b4e.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-2-c9d1b4e.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=599%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-2-c9d1b4e.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=899%2C599 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-2-c9d1b4e.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1199%2C799 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-2-c9d1b4e.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=299%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Cra