;resize=1661%2C1107 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=554%2C369, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1107%2C738 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1661%2C1107 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1859%2C1239 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 992px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1239%2C826 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1859%2C1239 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1631%2C1087 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=407%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=815%2C543 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1223%2C815 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1631%2C1087 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=555%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1110%2C740 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1667%2C1111 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Velo Orange Crazy Bar new 2021\" title=\"Velo Orange Crazy Bar new 2021\" src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/Velo-Orange-Crazy-Bar-update-1-6c66fce.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C413\"></picture></div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> The bar will be available later this year.</span></figcaption><p><span><i>Jack Luke / Immediate Media</i></span></p></div><p>Production has been delayed slightly, but the bar will be in stock at Velo Orange around June, and a pre-order period will likely open up before this date.</p><p>Pricing is TBC. Full details are available on <a href=\"https://velo-orange.blogspot.com/2021/02/the-next-generation-crazy-bars-first.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">the Velo Orange blog</a>.</p><section><div><h2>Who are Velo Orange’s Crazy bars for?</h2><p>A flat bar with a bit of sweep, a bit of rise and… aero-ish extensions? Just who the heck is this handlebar for?</p><p>While nominally designed as a touring bar, a handlebar of this style could make sense for a huge number of bikes.&nbsp;</p><p>For gravel bikes that sit at the gnarlier end of the shred spectrum, I reckon these could work well, if not better than standard drop bars. With the Crazy Bar, you’re getting all the control a flat bar offers and the added hand positions and aero benefits that come with the extensions.&nbsp;</p><p>Though the horns are a little widely spaced to adopt a truly aero position, they could even be useful for ultra-distance races on mixed terrain, though these riders may be better-served by typical bolt-on extensions and a normal flat bar.</p><p>The extensions also provide a useful area to secure luggage for any rider that likes to use a handlebar bag.&nbsp;</p><p>Of course, any rider will have to be comfortable with the not insignificant aesthetic challenge the bars present – no matter what bike you fit them to, these will be the standout feature, and you’ll have to be prepared to fend off questions from interested parties.&nbsp;</p><p>However, for those that favour practicality and comfort over all else, I think these could be a hit.&nbsp;</p></div><div><p><img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/PXL_20210131_161031625_2-14cfeaa.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=556,556\" srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/PXL_20210131_161031625_2-14cfeaa.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1025,1025 1025w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/PXL_20210131_161031625_2-14cfeaa.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=820,820 820w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/PXL_20210131_161031625_2-14cfeaa.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=615,615 615w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/PXL_20210131_161031625_2-14cfeaa.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=410,410 410w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/02/PXL_20210131_161031625_2-14cfeaa.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=205,205 205w,\" sizes=\"(min-width: 992px) 615px, (min-width: 768px) 410px, (min-width: 576px) 205px, calc(100vw - 20px)\" width=\"556\" height=\"556\" alt=\"Velo Orange Crazy Bar new 2021\" title=\"Velo Orange Crazy Bar new 2021\" data-source-name=\"Velo Orange\"></p><p></p><figcaption>Velo Orange</figcaption><p></p></div></section></section></div>","author":"Jack Luke","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"2ba1f7138097f3709ad3fa9bb863a0b6e4ed50763cec4a43b0313f4d591086c3","category":"Cycling"}